application.install-notice:
	  Example urls/topics/etc are installed, see the mmexamples page for the example pages.<br />
This application also installed the <strong>jumpers</strong> builder. The jumpers servlet uses
this builder to define url shortcuts.<br />
In order to install the jumpers servlet, you need to add the following code to your web.xml:<br />
<pre>
  &lt;filter&gt;
    &lt;filter-name&gt;Jumpers Filter&lt;/filter-name&gt;
    &lt;display-name&gt;Jumpers Filter&lt;/display-name&gt;
    &lt;description&gt;Filter used for jumpers&lt;/description&gt;
    &lt;filter-class&gt;org.mmbase.servlet.JumpersFilter&lt;/filter-class&gt;
  &lt;/filter&gt;

  &lt;filter-mapping&gt;
    &lt;filter-name&gt;Jumpers Filter&lt;/filter-name&gt;
    &lt;url-pattern&gt;/*&lt;/url-pattern&gt;
  &lt;/filter-mapping&gt;
</pre>
And restart your server.<br />
Note that this may not work in Orion 1.5.2 or lower.
See the release notes for more information on installing the jumpers servlet.
